OL,3,C'My heart is breaking': Sol Bamba's
OL,4,Cwife pays tribute after his death aged
OL,5,C39
OL,7,FSol Bamba's wife has paid tribute to
OL,8,Fher "hero" husband after the former
OL,9,FLeeds and Cardiff City defender died
OL,10,Faged 39.
OL,12,FBamba had been employed at Turkish
OL,13,Fclub Adanaspor, who announced the news
OL,14,Flate on Saturday night, 31 August.
OL,16,FA club statement said Bamba, who was
OL,17,Ftechnical director for the club, had
OL,18,Ffallen ill before a match and was
OL,19,Ftaken to hospital where he died.
