OL,3,C'My heart is breaking': Sol Bamba's
OL,4,Cwife pays tribute after his death aged
OL,5,C39
OL,7,FHis wife, Chloe, wrote on Instagram:
OL,8,F"For the last few years I have watched
OL,9,FSol fight his cancer head on with an
OL,10,Fastounding mental and physical
OL,11,Fstrength.
OL,13,F"Unfortunately, it was never a fair
OL,14,Ffight and just when things were
OL,15,Flooking up he took a downturn and
OL,16,Ffinally succumbed on 31st August.
OL,18,FShe said the past few years have been
OL,19,F"indescribably difficult" but the
OL,20,Fcouple "still managed to find joy and
OL,21,Flaughter."
