OL,3,C'My heart is breaking': Sol Bamba's
OL,4,Cwife pays tribute after his death aged
OL,5,C39
OL,7,FShe continued: "It was an honour to
OL,8,Fhave loved and been loved by Sol. I
OL,9,Flearnt so much form him. He is my
OL,10,Fhero. My heart is breaking. What a
OL,11,Fgift, what a gift to have been loved
OL,12,Fby him."
OL,14,FBamba was diagnosed with Non-Hodgkin
OL,15,Flymphoma in 2021 while at Cardiff, but
OL,16,Fwas declared cancer-free after a
OL,17,Fcourse of chemotherapy and returned to
OL,18,Fplay again for the Bluebirds and
OL,19,FMiddlesbrough.
