OL,5,C39
OL,7,FBamba made his debut for Leeds in 2015
OL,8,Fafter arriving at Elland Road on loan
OL,9,Ffrom Italian outfit Palmero.
OL,11,FAfter making 19 appearances for the
OL,12,FWhites during his loan spell, his move
OL,13,Fwas made permanent and he was made
OL,14,Fcaptain of the club ahead of the 2015/
OL,15,F16 season.
OL,17,FHis career also took in the likes of
OL,18,FLeicester, Hibernian and Dunfermline,
OL,19,Fin addition to 46 international
OL,20,Fappearances for the Ivory Coast.
