OL,3,C'My heart is breaking': Sol Bamba's
OL,4,Cwife pays tribute after his death aged
OL,5,C39
OL,7,FIn a statement a Leeds spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "One of the nicest people in
OL,9,Ffootball, the thoughts of everyone at
OL,10,FLeeds United are with Sol's family and
OL,11,Ffriends at this tragic time.
OL,13,F"Rest in peace Sol, you will forever
OL,14,Fbe in our hearts."
OL,16,FMiddlesbrough wrote: "We are
OL,17,Fdevastated to learn of the passing of
OL,18,FSol Bamba at the age of 39. Our
OL,19,Fthoughts are with Sol's family and
OL,20,Ffriends at this time. RIP Sol"
